{"type": "article", "id": 28053, "title": "不怕楼梯的行李箱", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-12T06:57:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 95, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702172640DuzI4agefAnF68LG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>带着拉杆箱出门，楼梯绝对是噩梦一般的存在。这款名为 TraxPack 的行李箱可以像坦克那样征服那些讨人厌的楼梯，奥秘就在于行李箱上增加的两条履带以及可以倾斜角度的拉杆。它还很贴心地自带称重功能，让你不用再担心行李超重的问题。除此之外，TraxPack 的背部还有一个可以拆卸的移动电源，你可以用倾斜的拉杆作为移动设备的支架，解放双手舒舒服服地看一场电影打发时间。这是它的众筹<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/traxpack/traxpack-luggage-worlds-first-stair-climbing-suitc/\">链接</a>，最低价为 198 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172636A2v70EaWJkih8IjO.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172638fA4rcQ7Cy3vS9aTd.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56222222\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172638t8dD0rje4yVmZM3n.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172639197xJTUH360vjXs4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56222222\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}